('loja_0110', '5354 Coffee', 'Culver’s Restaurant was founded by the Culver family in 1984, which eventually branched out to more than 300 franchised restaurants all over the US. Culver’s is well-known for its ButterBurger, which made the restaurant extremely famous. They also have other items which include salads, sandwiches, desserts, etc.', 'Italiana', 'https://picsum.photos/seed/loja_0110/400', true, 5.17, 25, 36, 3.6, 1821, 'Ponte Daniel Garcez', '617', 'São João da Madeira', 'AP', '06331235', 48.39571557, -67.21525016, NULL, '11:00 - 23:00', 'Fechado', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00'),
