('loja_0143', '664 Kitchen', 'Delhaize Group will achieve leading positions in food retailing in key mature and emerging markets. We accomplish our goal by developing strong regional companies benefiting from and contributing to the Groups strength, expertise and successful practices. Delhaize Group goes to market with a variety of food store formats. The Group is committed to offer a locally differentiated shopping experience to its customers in each of its markets, to deliver superior value and to maintain high social, environmental and ethical standards.', 'Japonesa', 'https://picsum.photos/seed/loja_0143/400', false, 11.72, 19, 40, 3.9, 156, 'Travessa Maitê da Cunha', 's/n', 'Moura', 'PI', '89205385', 51.32681417, -6.43684935, NULL, '11:00 - 23:00', 'Fechado', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00'),
