('loja_0396', 'Thirsty Burger', 'Culver’s Restaurant was founded by the Culver family in 1984, which eventually branched out to more than 300 franchised restaurants all over the US. Culver’s is well-known for its ButterBurger, which made the restaurant extremely famous. They also have other items which include salads, sandwiches, desserts, etc.', 'Saudável', 'https://picsum.photos/seed/loja_0396/400', false, 9.28, 29, 44, 4.4, 589, 'Rua Ladislau', '690', 'Rio Tinto', 'PA', '75571566', 36.69433262, -86.93196146, NULL, '11:00 - 23:00', 'Fechado', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00'),
