('loja_0757', '93 Dragon', 'Culver’s Restaurant was founded by the Culver family in 1984, which eventually branched out to more than 300 franchised restaurants all over the US. Culver’s is well-known for its ButterBurger, which made the restaurant extremely famous. They also have other items which include salads, sandwiches, desserts, etc.', 'Doces', 'https://picsum.photos/seed/loja_0757/400', true, 13.23, 24, 48, 4.0, 693, 'Marginal Luiz Otávio Monteira', '55667', 'Estarreja', 'MA', '23042338', 67.48944912, -1.59445692, NULL, '11:00 - 23:00', 'Fechado', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00', '11:00 - 23:00'),
